{"tid":1965812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［黃色經濟圈］請大家支持下黃店啦","createTime":"2020-04-09T17:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T03:05:02.000Z","uid":229185,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"31dc444e2fed28abeb438f60419f78366e70dbcc","tid":1965812,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T17:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rcsaQ9t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrcsaQ9t.jpg&h=d3566bc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日黃店榴槤樂園接受東網訪問，片段一出即引起網民討論。大家焦點都唔係放喺訪問內容，而係女店主嘅衣著&hellip;唔知係咪因為當日女店主知道要受訪，所以就突登著靚啲，雖然口罩一直遮著外貌，但結果仍成功吸晴～ 不過呢排生日真難做，係度希望大家生意精精溢上～<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（上面段野係copy)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkchronicles.com/data/0c8fdbc94e7b8f3a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkchronicles.com%2Fdata%2F0c8fdbc94e7b8f3a&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=fc95d118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkchronicles.com/data/0c8fdbc94e7b8f3a</a>"},{"pid":"f44ec57feff4aceea887203d9148100b08aab553","tid":1965812,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T17:25:53.000Z","msg":"十黃， 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2323e8494d38105b8fdc6cb0906a3b3970c210","tid":1965812,"uid":229185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T17:28:13.000Z","msg":"間店又黃， 人又黃， tui<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349c96797b952b1c68b648d209a08423cace0765","tid":1965812,"uid":349872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T17:28:46.000Z","msg":"我睇完呢幾張相都精精溢上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce138d768adde5cff5f018f5c3b909a0cfec3a76","tid":1965812,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T17:30:19.000Z","ms